<p>i have nested <code>ViewPager</code> in my <code>Fragment</code>. and want to manually switch the <code>Fragment</code> inside the <code>ViewPager</code>. I managed to do this successfully.</p>  <p>I disable the swipe by doing it like this. </p>  <pre><code>public class NonSwipeableViewPager extends ViewPager {      public NonSwipeableViewPager(Context context) {         super(context);     }      public NonSwipeableViewPager(Context context, AttributeSet attrs) {         super(context, attrs);     }      @Override     public boolean onInterceptTouchEvent(MotionEvent event) {         // Never allow swiping to switch between pages         return false;     }      @Override     public boolean onTouchEvent(MotionEvent event) {         // Never allow swiping to switch between pages         return false;     } } </code></pre>  <p>the problem is when i do it like this. i also disable the swipe of the parent tabs.</p>  <p>any idea? </p>